      "span_text": "These differences are explained by the intrinsic characteristics of the samples (people seeking care versus healthy citizens) and by the methods of recruitment adopted (convenience versus random sampling), as reported fully in Methods, and in a previously published paper. The implications of these differences are fully discussed in the Discussion."
